## âš ï¸ Common Errors & Fixes

| Error                   | Cause                         | Fix                                               |
| ----------------------- | ----------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------- |
| `RenderFlex overflowed` | Layout too small              | Use `SingleChildScrollView`                       |
| `No devices found`      | Emulator/device not connected | Start a device or use `flutter devices`           |
| `pubspec.yaml` error    | Indentation issue             | Use **2 spaces** and run `flutter pub get` again  |
| `Invalid email`         | Regex mismatch                | Ensure a valid email format like `name@email.com` |

